@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_ssiscm(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = wp.exp(0.32)
    v0 = ((wp.sin(tmp + 0.86) + (tmp + 0.91 / tmp + 0.55)) / (tmp / (v1 + 0.88 * v2 + 0.61)))
    v2 = v2
    tmp = (wp.exp(wp.sin(v1 + 0.84)) / (wp.sin(tmp + 0.79) * (v0 + 0.59 * tmp + 0.80)))
    v0 = wp.abs(wp.abs(wp.cos(v1 + 0.78)))
    v2 = wp.exp(wp.cos((v1 + 0.57 * v1 + 0.34)))
    tmp = (0.40 + wp.cos(0.94))
    v2 = v1
    data[tid] = v0
